text: Her onginnað þa capitulas þære forman bocedialogorumbe <haligra> wundrum.
Be Honorate þam cnihte, hu him wæs gemeted fisc on þam munte.
Be Libertine þam prafoste, hu he wearð of his horse aworpen.
Be Libertine, hu he næs funden, þeah þe he andweard wære.
Hu Libertinus awehte of deaðe sumes wifes sunu.
Be Libertines geþylde, þe he hæfde wið his abbod.
Be þam wyrtwearde, hu he bebead þære nædran þa wyrta to healdenne.
Be Equitio abbude, hu him wæs geþuht, þæt se engel hine belisnode.
Be Basilio, þe com to Equitie on muneclicum gyrelan.
Be þære nunfæmnan, þe bat þoone lahctuc.
Hu æquitius onfeng leafe to bodianne.
Be Equities gyrelan & þeawum.
Hu man <het> æquitium cuman to Rome.
Hu seo earc wæs aworpen of æquities byrigene.
Hu þa reðan Langbearde aweddon, & þa munecas þurh æquitium wurdon alysede.
Hu Constantius gefylde mid wætere þa leohtfatu & onælde & hy burnon.
Hu Constantius geþancode sumon ceorle, þæt he hine forseah.
Hu Marcellinus bisceop wæs asett ongean þæt fyr & hit acwanc.
Hu Nonnosus se prafost þone mycelan stanclud aweg adyde.
Hu Nonnosus þæt tobrokene glæsfæt on his gebede geedstaðelode.
Hu se ele weox under Nonnoses prafostscire.
Hu Anastasius & oðre seofon broðru wæron gecigde of þysum life.
Hu Bonefatius bisceop todælde win on fatu & hit weox.
Hu Bonefatius foresæde to sweltenne þone cimbalgliwere.
Hu Bonefatius þæs horses wurð todælde þearfum.
Hu Bonefatius þam Gotan gefyllde þa flaxan mid wine.
Hu Bonefatius afligde þa emelas.
Hu Bonefatius <forstæl> þone hwæte his meder & sealde þearfum, & æfter his gebede þæt bern wæs fulre, þonne hit ær wæs.
Hu Bonefatius mid his gebede adydde þone fox, þe bat his modor henna.
Hu Furtunatus þæt deofolseoke wif gehælde.
Hu Furtunatus þone awyrgedan gast adraf of sumum gedrehtum men.
Hu Furtunatus gehælde þone blindan & sum hors fram deofle.
Hu se Gota geneadod ageaf Furtunate þa cnihtas, & hu he awehte Marcellinum of deaðe.
Hu Martirius gemearcode þone hlaf.
Hu Seuerus se mæssepreost awehte of deaðe þone hiredes hlaford.
